Ghanaian actress, Yvonne Nelson, has revealed that the best way to enjoy marriage is to have a child with someone are not in love with. According to the actress ina recent interview with Hitz FM, she expressed that this would prevent heartbreak and emotional trauma when the other partners cheats. She said, “I feel like when you wanna have a kid, it should be even with someone you are not in love with because the moment the sole-called husband goes to cheat, you will catch feelings and start going mad.” -Advertisement- The actress further expressed that having a child with a partner you don’t love would create a platonic and simple relationship for the couple.